Triad Advisors
Confidence Wherever You Grow



Triad Hybrid Solutions is a Registered Investment Advisor firm offering the best features of an independent advice model. We provide expert consultative guidance, knowledgeable operational and compliance support, and advanced technology tools. Our solutions maximize efficiencies and foster growth.




Support for the Growing Independent Financial Advisor

Triad Hybrid Solutions is a Registered Investment Advisor firm providing the best features of an independent advice model, expert consultative and operational support, and advanced technology tools to improve efficiencies and foster growth. While we offer a flexible and proven back office RIA platform, we believe developing a strong relationship with advisors, one that gives us a true understanding of their vision, is the best way to build a sustainable and enjoyable business. 
In our ever-changing world of complex regulations and rapidly evolving technology, the management of an independent RIA entity is costly and distracts from client service and business growth. You must have confidence that you are meeting changing regulatory requirements and that you are keeping pace with technology. How else can you efficiently grow? But doing so requires full time expertise in compliance and technical advancements.



Compliance


Operations


Consultation


Performance
    Reporting/Trading


CRM


Triad Hybrid Solutions relieves the expense and headache of regulatory navigation by offering a flexible RIA structure that allows you to provide fee-based advice in your unique way. You may create your own branding and presence in the marketplace. We also provide performance reporting, trading, analytical and CRM solutions typically only accessible to the largest producing advisors in the industry.




Triad Hybrid Solutions presents an attractive alternative for advisors considering the outsourcing of compliance and technology support of their current RIA, especially if they are operating a state, or multi-state, registered RIA. Similarly, advisors looking to make a move from a bank, wirehouse or existing RIA, but are unsure of the pros and cons of establishing and running their own RIA, may find Triad Hybrid Solutions a perfect fit.
Contact Us
Contact us today and we will happily provide  an objective evaluation of your options.




Dual Registration

Triad Hybrid Solutions was created and is led by the same individuals who pioneered the “hybrid” advisor model through Triad Advisors, Inc., an industry-leading independent Broker Dealer. Dual registrants may choose to offer both fee and commission services associated with Triad Hybrid Solutions and Triad Advisors, respectively.
Learn more about your broker dealer options.




Triad Hybrid Solutions was created with the specific intent of allowing advisors to leverage the resources and pricing advantages of the largest RIA custodial platforms in the industry.
Triad Hybrid Solutions' executives have had relationships with our custodial partners for more than 15 years. Charles Schwab Advisor Services, Fidelity Institutional Wealth Services, and TD Ameritrade Institutional put you in the most competitive position to provide investment management to your existing and new clients. Together, we support you wherever you choose to grow.


Fidelity Institutional Wealth Services
Fidelity Institutional Wealth Services delivers a custody and clearing experience, and an actionable suite of offerings, designed to help advisors on the path to a high-performing firm. 


Charles Schwab Advisor Services
Charles Schwab has built their business on serving the needs of RIAs by providing a platform of institutional-caliber products, services and tools to deliver an exceptional experience to advisors and their clients.


TD Ameritrade Institutional *
TD Ameritrade Institutional is proud to support RIAs in their passionate pursuit of excellence by providing robust educational resources, comprehensive investment choices, and powerful technology tools.



* TD Ameritrade, Inc. is one of the firms that we use to custody our client assets. TD Ameritrade, Triad Hybrid Solutions, LLC, and the other entities named are separate and unaffiliated firms, and are not responsible for each other’s services or policies. TD Ameritrade does not endorse or recommend any advisor and the use of the TD Ameritrade name or logo does not represent the endorsement or recommendation of any advisor. Brokerage services provided by TD Ameritrade Institutional, Division of TD Ameritrade, Inc., member FINRA/SIPC. TD Ameritrade is a trademark jointly owned by TD Ameritrade IP Company, Inc. and The Toronto-Dominion Bank. Used with permission.





